the authenticity of the will?

107
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:31,240
I think you plotted to usurp the throne.

108
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,759
That's right. I disapprove of it.

109
00:16:36,519 --> 00:16:39,679
Gentlemen, before
the late emperor passed away,

110
00:16:39,879 --> 00:16:43,919
